message.content:
1. Breakfast: Oatmeal with fruit and nuts (no dairy) - add in a scoop of chia seeds for some extra protein
2. Lunch: Roast salmon with roasted veggies and quinoa or brown rice
3. Dinner: Chicken Stir-Fry with broccoli, mushrooms, and onions (no garlic)
4. Snacks: Fruit and nuts in between meals
5. Drinks: Water and tea
